full_threads.body:
Hi guys,

I have 2 requests regarding our properties please:

  1. We continue to have a recurring issue with the "New", "Occupied" and untagged properties displaying in a random order. Can we please look into a more permanent solution that reliably ensures this does not keep reordering, as I find this pops up every month or so. As mentioned we want new properties to display first, untagged second, and occupied last.
  2. I'd like to introduce some new tags please. In addition to "NEW" and "OCCUPIED" I would like to have two new ones created: "AVAILABLE" and "COMING SOON". The style for display I have indicated in the attachments. Moving forward I want all properties to show at least one of these tags, with the ability to toggle between them. Can I ask you to put some hours toward this?
Ideally I would like the first item actioned ASAP if you can please.

Thank you!

Regards,
Joshua Cook​​​​
Marketing Manager, Disability Services
